Release Manager Checklist
=========================

While making releases, make sure you have done
the following:

* pom.xml version change

* src/main/resources/org/wiztools/jenkryptor/ABOUT
  Change version here. Update the text if need be.

* Change Log level to INFO in this file:
  src/main/resources/org/wiztools/jenkryptor/logging.properties

* Tag the release

* Generate site, update in WizTools.org

* BerliOS.de --> file release

* FreshMeat.net --> announce


